$ npx create-react-app blogapp
  Success! Created blogapp

$ npm start
  Compiled successfully!
  Local: http://localhost:3000

------------------------------------------------------------
LIFECYCLE SEQUENCE
------------------------------------------------------------
  1. constructor()         → State initialized: posts=[], loading=true
  2. render()              → Renders "Loading posts from API..."
  3. componentDidMount()   → Calls loadPosts() → fetch() triggered
     → GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts → 200 OK
     → 100 posts received, sliced to first 10
     → setState({ posts: [...], loading: false })
  4. render()              → Re-renders with 10 posts displayed
  [Error scenario]
  5. componentDidCatch()   → alert("An error occurred...")

